{"tid":2383782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳業坤去日本Working Holiday 兩個月來零工作","createTime":"2021-01-28T06:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T11:59:16.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa91858df371fe956e2c21369e8a62fa9473c34","tid":2383782,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"現年30歲的吳業坤，近期少有露面，原來他去年11月去了日本Working Holiday體驗一下異地生活。不過坤哥去到當地兩個月，至今仍然未搵到工，仲每日瞓到黃朝百晏，完全抱住佛系心態去享受「0工作假期」。<br />\n<br />\n吳業坤去年踏30歲，趁住自己未超齡，就於去年11月飛到日本進行Working Holiday，至今已經兩個幾月。早前他接受鄭裕玲電台節目訪問，卻自爆自己兩個月以來都是零工作，表示：「日日瞓到自然醒，瞓醒都10點幾」生活亦平平無奇，他續道「開頭都諗住搵工，但係唔知幾時返香港，所以算啦，變咗no working嘅working holiday。」<br />\n<br />\n而Do姐聽到坤哥如此佛系搵工，都睇唔過眼，提議他拍片分享在日本的生活點滴。豈料坤哥坦言自己未體驗到甚麼，生活也欠缺衝擊，無謂勉強自己拍片，又自嘲自己來到日本只帶了幾萬元，覺得「應該夠用」。<br />\n<br />\n去working holiday去到如此隨心無所謂，Do姐忍不住問：「唔悶咩？」坤哥此時再講：「有啲思鄉嘅，原來兩個月唔工作，都有諗覺得自己好似好廢。」看來坤哥要努力一點去搵工先得。"},{"pid":"a57cd46a35a6b25d2285418e6244ab9ceabf2227","tid":2383782,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"廢佬"},{"pid":"a239fdd47f39a8bd48730cd0508fff5558bfbff5","tid":2383782,"uid":78243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"有錢仲打咩工﹐傻的嗎仔"},{"pid":"acc22e39cfb84154d57ca14a4744e43191b5f601","tid":2383782,"uid":198216,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"日日去飛田新地"},{"pid":"037d69499538dbf87921d14269960711454ea7d6","tid":2383782,"uid":111253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"acc22e39cfb84154d57ca14a4744e43191b5f601","tid":2383782,"uid":198216,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"日日去飛田新地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"真 個樣仁能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8ff618e2d2e1f9eccd6d5899ebc37629d1a26","tid":2383782,"uid":39316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"我當年黎working holiday頭半年都無做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實平凡咁住係日本，得閒先出去玩下，洗費唔係好高"},{"pid":"9857bc1e956677aba6085ba89639a3529ad30402","tid":2383782,"uid":28068,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"咁同佢係香港好似差唔多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47fa378f9e19293eef9dec34e24f49210805e62","tid":2383782,"uid":83328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"佢搵咁多, 當旅行咋, 仲同你打份牛工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f695d71787cb37851ee7a333d0cc299a3525943","tid":2383782,"uid":122798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"唔好返黎 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b438fb219f0fe0cfdd779c75b4d86dfb70d671d3","tid":2383782,"uid":256246,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"傻西瓜先會working holiday真係去做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717634db71e93c51535ee64aeef67d8ce08d0c52","tid":2383782,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"佢大把錢洗鬼打工咩"},{"pid":"7b6202be9f862a8cfca2eb022a68be141b507801","tid":2383782,"uid":387907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"工又唔搵<br />\n生活體驗又無<br />\n<br />\n咁佢去working holiday 嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5989e4cbd25eabdb0cc69d69161bf3821d4bbe8","tid":2383782,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"起碼返下語言學校學下日文識下人<br />\n話唔定識到條日本妹唔洗返香港"},{"pid":"54c6da0d15da414b449c17fa9d8429157ffa91e4","tid":2383782,"uid":15625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"唔搵佢老友賤吾幫手呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.